                <p>I. <hi rend="italic">Record of a Previous Meeting</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Record of the Fourth Meeting was <hi rend="italic">referred back</hi> to the
                    Secretariat.</p>
                <p>II. <hi rend="italic">Italo-Yugoslav Frontier</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council continued its study of the Italo-Yugoslav frontier.</p>
                <p>III. The Ministers agreed to meet informally on Sunday, May the 5th in Mr.
                    Bidault’s office under his chairmanship./.</p>
